transcription.text:
Speaker 1: Thank you for calling Viagra, how can I help you?

Speaker 2: Yes, my name is Carlos Rodriguez and I'd like to cancel the recurring refills that you have on me.

Speaker 1: Sure, no problem. I can help you out.

Speaker 2: Can I just have your phone number so I can pull up your account?

Speaker 1: Sure, 863-464-0361.

Speaker 2: Thank you, Carlos.

Speaker 1: Can you just confirm your date of birth?

Speaker 2: My 2/15/59.

Speaker 1: Thank you so much.

Speaker 2: I see you're a VIP status customer, and how's the medication working out for you?

Speaker 1: It works fine.

Speaker 2: I just don't need to be refilled every month.

Speaker 1: Oh, okay.

Speaker 2: I mean, I'm 67 years old.

Speaker 1: Oh, no problem.

Speaker 2: So, yeah, with your VIP status, you don't have to have your refills on a monthly basis.

Speaker 1: What a lot of people like to do is just go ahead and pause it for a few months.

Speaker 2: That way, it keeps your prescription active and just allows you to call in whenever you need a refill.

Speaker 1: I could pause that for you.

Speaker 2: That's what I will.

Speaker 1: Yeah, that'd be great.

Speaker 2: I mean, because I know you got one already being sent another one to me.

Speaker 1: I was checking my checking account.

Speaker 2: I said, well, they went ahead and sent me another one and I still got four pills left of the other one.

Speaker 1: No, five pills left still, so I'm okay right now, so.

Speaker 2: Okay, no problem.

Speaker 1: I went ahead and paused you until June 1st, so if you don't need a refill by then, just give us a call and you can pause it further.

Speaker 2: Okay, thank you.

Speaker 1: No problem.

Speaker 2: I appreciate that very much.

Speaker 1: Yeah, of course.

Speaker 2: No problem.

Speaker 1: Bye.
